@startuml sequence_diagram_kelola_pengguna
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram Kelola Pengguna\nSistem Prediksi Penyebaran DBD

actor "Admin" as User
participant "Halaman\nPengguna" as Page
participant "Controller\nUser" as Controller
database "Database" as DB

== Menampilkan Daftar Pengguna ==

User -> Page : Buka menu Kelola Pengguna
activate Page

Page -> Controller : Request daftar pengguna
activate Controller

Controller -> DB : SELECT * FROM users
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Return data users
deactivate DB

Controller --> Page : Kirim data users
Page --> User : Tampilkan tabel pengguna

deactivate Controller

== Tambah Pengguna Baru ==

User -> Page : Klik tombol Tambah
Page --> User : Tampilkan form input

User -> Page : Input data:\n- Username\n- Password\n- Nama Lengkap\n- Email\n- Role

Page -> Controller : Submit form
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller : Validasi username unik
Controller -> DB : SELECT * WHERE username = ?
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Return result
deactivate DB

alt Username tersedia
    Controller -> Controller : Hash password
    Controller -> DB : INSERT INTO users
    activate DB
    DB --> Controller : Success
    deactivate DB
    
    Controller -> DB : INSERT log_aktivitas
    Controller --> Page : Response sukses
    Page --> User : Tampilkan alert sukses
    
else Username sudah ada
    Controller --> Page : Response error
    Page --> User : Tampilkan pesan error
end

deactivate Controller

== Ubah Status Pengguna ==

User -> Page : Klik toggle status
Page -> Controller : Request update status
activate Controller

Controller -> DB : UPDATE users SET status = ?
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Success
deactivate DB

Controller --> Page : Response sukses
Page --> User : Refresh status
deactivate Controller

== Hapus Pengguna ==

User -> Page : Klik tombol Hapus
Page --> User : Konfirmasi hapus

User -> Page : Konfirmasi Ya
Page -> Controller : Request delete
activate Controller

Controller -> DB : DELETE FROM users WHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Success
deactivate DB

Controller --> Page : Response sukses
Page --> User : Refresh halaman
deactivate Controller

deactivate Page

@enduml
